{"tid":830140,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"小雙俠扮乘客扑7的士9　掠走5000元財物","createTime":"2018-09-21T03:23:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-21T16:42:57.000Z","uid":184679,"like":9,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"52bfd32fdc400d5bc6cb094a6f7e2e27ab5127a4","tid":830140,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T03:23:31.000Z","msg":"昨日(20日)晚上10時許，警方接獲一名46歲姓張的士司機報案，指於上水新運路接載2名戴上口罩年約20至30歲的男女，當駛至打鼓嶺坪輋路近大埔田時，2男女乘客以硬物襲擊的哥，並劫去約650港元現金、1隻價值500港元的手錶及2部總值約3,500港元的手提電話，2賊人得手後逃去。的哥負傷報警，他手及額頭受傷，其後自行前往那打素醫院求醫。<br />\n<br />\n警方接報到案發現場調查，案件暫列行劫，交由大埔警區刑事調查隊跟進，暫未有人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180921/bkn-20180921051051341-0921_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180921%2Fbkn-20180921051051341-0921_00822_001.html&d=P5LHX3D3HIDgOzZmlaQVvcVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=6896259b\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180921/bkn-20180921051051341-0921_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"0c2d008a43a9dc99f8e7c0a0de14fd523b01252f","tid":830140,"uid":166886,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T03:28:12.000Z","msg":"乜撚野的哥，叫埋運將好唔撚好"},{"pid":"72801ebaddc92eb2da1c0856542ab125cb0e8d2c","tid":830140,"uid":32342,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T03:42:43.000Z","msg":"的乜9哥 用撚埋大佬音當有趣"},{"pid":"25b4b69de85102e5e0a4325c92c92c03f51d78fb","tid":830140,"uid":32342,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"72801ebaddc92eb2da1c0856542ab125cb0e8d2c","tid":830140,"uid":32342,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T03:42:43.000Z","msg":"的乜9哥 用撚埋大佬音當有趣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T03:43:07.000Z","msg":"陸"},{"pid":"f28b41f51dd2901499b44192e6280c89e3778e49","tid":830140,"uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T04:22:42.000Z","msg":"哥Auntie<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efe8fe45